{{Infobox recurring event | name =Sarajevo StreeAt Food Festival | native_name = | native_name_lang = | logo = | logo_alt = | logo_caption = | logo_size = | image = File:Sarajevo.streeat.food.festival.png | image_size = | alt = | caption = | status = active | genre = [[Food festival]] | date = <!-- {{start date|YYYY|mm|dd}} "dates=" also works, but do not use both --> | begins = <!-- {{start date|YYYY|mm|dd}} --> | ends = <!-- {{end date|YYYY|mm|dd}} --> | frequency = Annually | venue = | location = Sarajevo | coordinates = <!-- {{coord|LAT|LON|type:event|display=inline,title}} --> | country = Bosnia and Herzegovina | years_active = 2018 - present | first = <!-- {{start date|YYYY|mm|dd}} "founded=" and "established=" also work --> | founder_name = Pro Optimus Tours | last = <!-- Date of most recent event; if the event will not be held again, use {{End date|YYYY|MM|DD|df=y}} --> | prev = | next = | participants = | attendance = | capacity = | area = | budget = | activity = | leader_name = | patron = | organised = <!-- "organized=" also works --> | filing = | people = | member = | sponsor = <!-- | or sponsors = --> | website = {{URL|http://ssff.ba/}} | footnotes = }} The '''Sarajevo StreeAt Food Festival''' ({{lang-bs|Festival ulične hrane Sarajevo / Фестивал уличне хране Сарајево}}) is an annual international [[street food|street]] [[food festival]] held in [[Sarajevo]], [[Bosnia and Herzegovina]]. <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.klix.ba/lifestyle/hranaipice/prvi-sarajevo-streeat-food-festival-od-27-jula-do-17-augusta/180702060|title=Prvi Sarajevo Streeat Food Festival od 27. jula do 17. augusta|publisher=klix.ba}}</ref> <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sarajevotimes.com/first-sarajevo-streeat-food-festival-officially-started/|title=First Sarajevo StreeAt Food Festival officially started|publisher=sarajevotimes.com}}</ref> It is held in July and August of every year and lasts for three weeks. <ref>{{cite web|url=https://senzacija.ba/2018/07/20/sarajevo-street-food-festival-pocinje-27-jula/|title=Sarajevo Streeat Food Festival počinje 27. jula|publisher=senzacija.ba}}</ref> The festival was established in 2018 by Pro Optimus Tours and is the only one of its kind in Bosnia and Herzegovina. <ref>{{cite web|url=http://zdraviportal.ba/posjetitelji-na-sarajevo-street-food-festivalu-uzivaju-u-delicijama-i-zabavi/|title=Posjetitelji na Sarajevo Streeat Food Festivalu uživaju u delicijama i zabavi |publisher=zdraviportal.ba}}</ref>
The festival's main venue is Alija Izetbegović Square in downtown Sarajevo where it presents both national and international street food showcased by over 100 different vendors. <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sutra.ba/vijest/domaa-hrana-i-dobrodolica-gostima-grada-163481#facebookPopup|title=Domaća hrana i dobrodošlica gostima grada|publisher=sutra.ba}}</ref> The festival's programme also includes nightly rock concerts, after-work parties, [[Electronic Dance Music|EDM sessions]], cooking workshops for school children and adults, cuisine-themed open air film screenings, a cooking book trade fair and the filming of live cooking shows for television. <ref>{{cite web|url=http://ssff.ba/|title=About us|publisher=official website}}</ref> <ref>{{cite web|url=http://ba.n1info.com/a274256/Video/Pocinje-prvi-Sarajevo-Streeat-Food-festival.html|title=Počinje prvi Sarajevo Streeat Food festival|publisher=ba.n1info.com}}</ref> The 2018 edition attracted over 200,000 visitors. <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.klix.ba/lifestyle/hranaipice/prvi-sarajevo-streeat-food-festival-od-27-jula-do-17-augusta/180702060|title=Prvi Sarajevo Streeat Food Festival od 27. jula do 17. augusta|publisher=klix.ba}}</ref>
